Library

library(csaw)
library(edgeR)
library(ChIPseeker)
library(ggplotify)
library(TxDb.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10.knownGene)
library(org.Mm.eg.db)
library(EnrichedHeatmap)

TxDb and Promoter

txdb <- TxDb.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10.knownGene
promoter <- getPromoters(TxDb = txdb, upstream = 1000, downstream = 1000)
regions <- getPromoters(TxDb = txdb, upstream = 5000, downstream = 5000)

All peaks

Reading the peak file

allAtac <- GRanges(read.table("input/PND_Adult_NF_peaks.narrowPeak",
  header = F,
  col.names = c(
    "Chr", "Start", "End", "Name", "Score", "Strand",
    "FoldChange", "negLog10pvalue", "negLog10qvalue",
    "Summit"
  ), stringsAsFactors = F
))

PNDAtac <- GRanges(read.table("input/PND15_NF_peaks.narrowPeak",
  header = F,
  col.names = c(
    "Chr", "Start", "End", "Name", "Score", "Strand",
    "FoldChange", "negLog10pvalue", "negLog10qvalue",
    "Summit"
  ), stringsAsFactors = F
))

AdultAtac <- GRanges(read.table("input/Adult_NF_peaks.narrowPeak",
  header = F,
  col.names = c(
    "Chr", "Start", "End", "Name", "Score", "Strand",
    "FoldChange", "negLog10pvalue", "negLog10qvalue",
    "Summit"
  ), stringsAsFactors = F
))

Analysis

tagMatrix.all <- getTagMatrix(allAtac, windows = regions)

tagPlot <- as.ggplot(~ tagHeatmap(
    tagMatrix = tagMatrix.all, xlim = c(-5000, 5000),
    color = "red", title = "All peaks"
))

peakAnno.all <- annotatePeak(peak = allAtac, 
                             TxDb = txdb, 
                             tssRegion = c(-1000, 1000), 
                             annoDb = "org.Mm.eg.db")
## >> preparing features information...      2020-01-15 04:49:27 PM 
## >> identifying nearest features...        2020-01-15 04:49:28 PM 
## >> calculating distance from peak to TSS...   2020-01-15 04:49:33 PM 
## >> assigning genomic annotation...        2020-01-15 04:49:33 PM 
## >> adding gene annotation...          2020-01-15 04:49:49 PM 
## >> assigning chromosome lengths           2020-01-15 04:49:49 PM 
## >> done...                    2020-01-15 04:49:49 PM
pie <- as.ggplot(~plotAnnoPie(peakAnno.all))
barPlot <- plotAnnoBar(peakAnno.all)
tssPlot <- plotDistToTSS(peakAnno.all)
upset <- upsetplot(peakAnno.all, vennpie = TRUE)
avgProfile <- plotAvgProf(tagMatrix.all, xlim = c(-5000, 5000), conf = 0.95, resample = 100)
## >> Running bootstrapping for tag matrix...        2020-01-15 04:51:08 PM
allPeaks <- list(tagMatrix = tagMatrix.all,
                 peakAnno = peakAnno.all,
                 tagsPlot = tagPlot,
                 barPlot = barPlot,
                 tssPlot = tssPlot,
                 upsetPlot = upset,
                 avgProfile = avgProfile,
                 pieChart = pie)

Differential accessible regions (peaks)

Reading the data

load("./input/atac_diff_chromatin_accessibility.RData")
da <- data.frame(rowData(data), stringsAsFactors = F, check.names = F)
da <- da[(da$`diffAccessibility-logFC` >= 1 | da$`diffAccessibility-logFC` <= -1) &
           da$`diffAccessibility-qvalue` <= 0.05,]

colnames(da)[1:5] <- gsub(pattern = "Peak-", replacement = "", x = colnames(da)[1:5])

da.GR <- GRanges(da)

Differential Accessible regions (all)

Analysis

tagMatrix.da <- getTagMatrix(da.GR, windows = regions)

tagPlot <- as.ggplot(~ tagHeatmap(
    tagMatrix = tagMatrix.da, xlim = c(-5000, 5000),
    color = "red", title = "Differential accessible peaks"
))

peakAnno.da <- annotatePeak(peak = da.GR, 
                             TxDb = txdb, 
                             tssRegion = c(-1000, 1000), 
                             annoDb = "org.Mm.eg.db")
